{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "hr_team", "channel": "employee_retention", "user": "sarah_jones", "message": "I just received feedback from the recent employee satisfaction survey. We should discuss the key points in our next HR meeting.", "create_at": 1693647600000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "marketing_team", "channel": "content_strategy", "user": "mike_adams", "message": "I think we should allocate a part of our budget for a digital campaign focusing on mental health awareness. What do you all think?", "create_at": 1693651200000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "hr_team", "channel": "employee_retention", "user": "sarah_jones", "message": "I also want to discuss our upcoming training sessions for new hires. We need to ensure they have all the resources they need from day one.", "create_at": 1693654800000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "marketing_team", "channel": "content_strategy", "user": "ryan_thompson", "message": "I\u2019ll be attending the upcoming healthcare technology conference. It could be a great opportunity to network and gather insights for our next projects.", "create_at": 1693658400000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "hr_team", "channel": "employee_retention", "user": "sarah_jones", "message": "Let\u2019s also review our current onboarding process. There are a few areas where we could enhance the experience for new employees.", "create_at": 1693662000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "marketing_team", "channel": "content_strategy", "user": "mike_adams", "message": "Has anyone seen the latest customer feedback on our telehealth platform? It might help us shape our next campaign.", "create_at": 1693665600000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "hr_team", "channel": "employee_retention", "user": "sarah_jones", "message": "I think we should schedule a performance review cycle soon. It\u2019s important to ensure everyone is on track with their goals.", "create_at": 1693669200000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "hr_team", "channel": "employee_retention", "user": "sarah_jones", "message": "Hey team, I just completed the analysis for Q3 2024. Our employee turnover rate for this quarter is 12%. This indicates we have a stable workforce retention, which is great news for our ongoing projects and overall company morale. It\u2019s essential to highlight this stability as we move forward with our recruitment strategies. Maintaining a solid team is crucial for our patient attraction strategies, even if it doesn\u2019t directly relate to marketing efforts.", "create_at": 1698326400000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "marketing_team", "channel": "content_strategy", "user": "ryan_thompson", "message": "Thanks for the update, Sarah! That\u2019s reassuring to hear about the turnover rate. It\u2019s important for us in marketing to understand that a stable team helps us communicate our brand effectively and maintain the quality of our services. Let\u2019s make sure to incorporate this positive outlook into our upcoming campaigns.", "create_at": 1698326500000}}
